name: Memento Mauri #14
description: This Free Spirit can never be tamed, no matter the institution or rigorous military camp her Family stuffed her into. After years of dodging the attempts at changing her Wild approach to life, she fled to Animus' Underworld. The Motley Family found her gusto to be quite amusing, putting her to work immediately on the streets as an Enforcer and Debt Collector. Her weapon of Choice? "BONK": A Two Handed, Helforged Steel Warhammer, Coated in a Custom Enamel for the appearance of a Child's Squeaky Toy. The scratches are a personal record for how many "Home-Runs" she hits, using her opponents Cranium as a ball.
